# ZeroAuth Governance — Code Owners
#
# Path-based ownership. Every PR is reviewed by at least one owner of every
# path it touches. For files under `docs/shared/` and `docs/compliance/`, two
# reviewers are required (Pulkit + Amit; counsel as well for DPDP-touching).
#
# Counsel review is enforced manually (not via CODEOWNERS) because counsel
# does not have GitHub access; reviewers note counsel sign-off in the PR
# description before merging policy-touching changes.

